  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Subject Line: Overdue Payment

    From: Susan



    Hey, it''s your
    landlord. Heard about your cushy job at I.E.R.F. Good thing, now you can pay
    me back. Although I heard a lot of people go missing in those jobs. You better
    keep yourself safe; no one''s gonna be there to take care of your sister. Anyways,
    like yesterday, I''ll be needing $300 again.



    Much Love,

    Susan

'
