  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Subject Line: Welcome to the IERF Family



    FROM: I.E.R.F. Human Resources



    Welcome
    to I.E.R.F. or the [INTERNATIONAL ENTITY RESISTANCE FORCE]. Here at I.E.R.F,
    we put our clients first. That means you, our latest addition to the family,
    must do your best to deliver accurate information and help our clients with their
    entity issues. You must submit the right information to your clients based on
    their observations. You''d better do your best, we wouldn''t want anyone dying
    on us now, would we? Also, keep in mind that, as per usual, your accuracy rate
    will determine your wage for the day, so do your best.

    Thank you for your
    service. See you soon.



    Sincerely,

    I.E.R.F. Human Resources

'
