  m_text: '

    Subject Line: Overdue Rent



    From: Susan



    Hey, it''s
    your landlord. I know times are tough, and I''ve already turned a blind eye to
    your last overdue payment. I let that one slide mostly because of your sick sister,
    but I really can''t tolerate this much longer. I need $300 by today.



    Much
    love,

    Susan

'
